title: Looking for a duo, Pref an adc main.

embed.description: Create & discover new Champion builds/strategies, check your Summoner statistics and try our powerful LoL charts.

body:
I'm looking for a duo partner for bot lane so an adc main, Just need to a little help getting from S1 to G5 willing to play longer if you want to.
My mains are Janna,thresh and leo.

replies.body: you should try Sona out she's a really op supp, build ap for her. Coming from a supp/adc main :D
